<h2>Adding Books</h2>
<p>
dslibris will find all XHTML files with extensions .xht or .xhtml that are in your media's /book directory. These books will show up in the book browser.
</p>

<h2>Library Controls</h2>

<ul>
<li>Select a book: [DPAD-UP] and [DPAD-DOWN].</li>
<li>Open selected book: [A], [TAP], or [DPAD-RIGHT].</li>
<li>Return to the last open book: [START].</li>
</ul>

<h2>Reading Controls</h2>

<ul>
<li>Advance one page: [A],[R*],[DPAD-RIGHT] or [TAP] on on the right half of the touchscreen.</li>
<li>Retreat one page: [B],[L*],[DPAD-LEFT] or [TAP] on the left half of the touchscreen.</li>
<li>Cycle through screen brightness on DS Lite: [Y].</li>
<li>Enter Library: [SELECT].</li>
</ul>

* [L] and [R] are reversed when the display is in flipped over into "left-hand" mode.

</body>
